  "text": "We used the Austronesian Basic Vocabulary Database [CITATION_1] as the basis for a series of experiments used to evaluate the performance of our system and the factors relevant to its success. The database includes partial cognacy judgments and IPA transcriptions, as well as a few reconstructed protolanguages. A reconstruction of Proto-Oceanic (POc) originally developed by Blust (1993) using the comparative method was the basis for evaluation.",
